<div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h3>ğŸ’¡ Hardware Best Practices:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Static Electricity:</b> Always ground yourself before handling components</li>
