<div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h3>ğŸ’¡ Power & Memory Best Practices:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><b>PSU Headroom:</b> Always plan for 20-30% more wattage than calculated peak</li>
        <li><b>Efficiency Sweet Spot:</b> PSUs are most efficient at 40-60% load</li>
        <li><b>RAM Configuration:</b> Use matched sticks in correct slots for dual/quad channel</li>
        <li><b>Heat Management:</b> RAM generates heat too - ensure proper airflow</li>
