                <li>Memory: 4096 MB (4GB)</li>
                <li>Hard disk: Create virtual disk now</li>
                <li>File type: VDI (VirtualBox Disk Image)</li>
                <li>Storage: Dynamically allocated</li>
                <li>Size: 25 GB</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        
        <li><b>Configure VM Settings:</b>
            <ul>
                <li>System â†’ Processor: 2 CPUs</li>
                <li>Display â†’ Video Memory: 128 MB</li>
