<b>GPT Advantages:</b>
â€¢ Supports up to 128 primary partitions (no extended/logical needed)
â€¢ Maximum disk size: 9.4 ZB (zettabytes = billion terabytes!)
â€¢ Uses 64-bit LBA addressing (no CHS limitations)
â€¢ CRC32 checksums for header and partition table (error detection)
â€¢ Backup copy at end of disk (redundancy)
â€¢ Each partition has unique GUID (globally unique identifier)
â€¢ Stores partition names (human-readable labels)
