    <div style="background-color: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">
            <h5>Linux Permission Breakdown</h5>
            <pre style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; text-align: left;">
-rwxr-xr--  1 alice  developers  4096 Mar 15 10:30 script.sh
â”‚â””â”€â”¬â”€â”˜â””â”€â”¬â”€â”˜ â””â”€â”€â”¬â”€â”€â”˜ â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¬â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜       â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¬â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜
â”‚  â”‚    â”‚      â”‚         â”‚                  â”‚
â”‚  â”‚    â”‚      â”‚         â”‚                  â””â”€â”€ File Name
â”‚  â”‚    â”‚      â”‚         â””â”€â”€ Size (bytes)
â”‚  â”‚    â”‚      â””â”€â”€ Group Owner
â”‚  â”‚    â””â”€â”€ User Owner
â”‚  â””â”€â”€ Permissions String
â””â”€â”€ File Type (- = file, d = directory, l = link)

PERMISSIONS STRING: -rwxr-xr--
Position: 123456789
1: File type (-, d, l, etc.)
2-4: User (owner) permissions: rwx = read, write, execute
5-7: Group permissions: r-x = read, execute, no write
8-10: Other (world) permissions: r-- = read only, no write/execute

NUMERIC (OCTAL) NOTATION:
r = 4, w = 2, x = 1
rwx = 4+2+1 = 7
r-x = 4+0+1 = 5
r-- = 4+0+0 = 4
-rwxr-xr-- = 754
