            "4-1": {
                icon: "fa-network-wired",
                title: "Introduction to Networking & OSI 7 Layers",
                html: `<h1>Week 4, Day 1: Introduction to Networking & OSI 7 Layers</h1>
        <p>Today we begin our journey into networking by understanding how data travels across networks and mastering the OSI 7-layer model.</p>

        <div class="analogy-box">
