            Switches: Mail sorting centers<br />
            Protocols: Postal service rules<br />
            OSI Layers: Different departments in the postal service
        </div>

        <h3>What is a Computer Network?</h3>
        <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 10px;">
            <h4>ğŸŒ Network Components Overview</h4>

            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;">
                <tr style="background: #4A90E2; color: white;">
                    <th style="padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Component</th>
