        </div>

        <h3>The OSI 7-Layer Model</h3>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
                <h4>ğŸ“Š OSI Model Layers (Top-Down)</h4>
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr style="background: #2c3e50; color: white;">
                        <th style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Layer</th>
                        <th style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Name</th>
                        <th style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Protocols</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">7</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Application</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">HTTP, FTP, SMTP, DNS</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background: white;">
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">6</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Presentation</td>
