            <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 10px;">
                <h5>How DHCP Reservations Work:</h5>
                <ol>
                    <li>Client MAC address is recorded in DHCP server</li>
                    <li>Specific IP is reserved for that MAC</li>
                    <li>Client gets same IP via normal DHCP process</li>
                    <li>IP stays consistent but can be managed centrally</li>
                </ol>

                <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #f8d7da; border-radius: 5px;">
                    <h6>Reservation Example:</h6>
