MAC Address: 00:1A:2B:3C:4D:5E
Reserved IP: 192.168.1.25
Hostname: Conference-Room-PC
Description: PC in main conference room
                </pre>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #fff3cd; border-radius: 5px;">
