                    <p><b>Requirements:</b> 10 router links, each needs 2 hosts</p>

                    <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #e8f5e8; border-radius: 5px;">
                        <h6>Solution: Use /30 subnets</h6>
                        <p>Each /30 gives 2 usable hosts (perfect for router links)</p>
                        <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 0.8em;">
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding: 5px;">Link 1:</td>
