# UAC Levels (Registry: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Policies\System)
# ConsentPromptBehaviorAdmin values:
# 0 - No prompt (disabled, not recommended)
# 1 - Prompt for credentials on secure desktop
# 2 - Prompt for consent on secure desktop (default)
# 3 - Prompt for credentials
# 4 - Prompt for consent
