            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><b>Role-Based Access Control:</b>
            <ul>
                <li>Predefined roles with specific privileges</li>
                <li>Time-based restrictions (students only during class hours)</li>
                <li>Application whitelisting/blacklisting per role</li>
                <li>Network access controls by role</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><b>Auditing and Monitoring:</b>
            <ul>
                <li>Login/logout tracking</li>
                <li>Privilege escalation logging</li>
                <li>File access monitoring for sensitive areas</li>
                <li>Real-time alerting for suspicious activities</li>
