<h3>The Attack Lifecycle (Cyber Kill Chain)</h3>
<div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 10px;">
    <h4>ğŸ”— Lockheed Martin Cyber Kill Chain</h4>
    
    <pre style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
1. RECONNAISSANCE - Research and identification
   â€¢ Gather information about target
   â€¢ Identify vulnerabilities
   â€¢ Methods: Social media, websites, network scanning
   
2. WEAPONIZATION - Create attack package
   â€¢ Combine exploit with backdoor
   â€¢ Create malicious document/executable
   â€¢ Methods: Malware creation, exploit development
   
3. DELIVERY - Transmit weapon to target
   â€¢ Send phishing email
   â€¢ Upload to compromised website
   â€¢ Methods: Email, USB drops, web drive-by
   
4. EXPLOITATION - Trigger the exploit
   â€¢ Open malicious attachment
   â€¢ Click malicious link
   â€¢ Methods: Code execution, vulnerability exploitation
   
5. INSTALLATION - Install malware/backdoor
   â€¢ Establish foothold in system
   â€¢ Create persistence mechanism
   â€¢ Methods: Registry changes, service installation
   
6. COMMAND & CONTROL (C2) - Remote control
   â€¢ Establish communication channel
   â€¢ Receive commands from attacker
   â€¢ Methods: HTTP, DNS, encrypted channels
   
7. ACTIONS ON OBJECTIVES - Complete mission
   â€¢ Data exfiltration
   â€¢ System destruction
   â€¢ Methods: Data theft, ransomware deployment

Example: NotPetya Ransomware Attack
1. Recon: Identify Ukrainian accounting software users
2. Weaponize: Create malware-laced software update
3. Delivery: Push through legitimate update server
4. Exploit: Execute when software updates
5. Install: Encrypt master boot records
6. C2: Communicate encryption status
7. Objectives: Destroy systems, demand ransom
    </pre>
    
    <h4>ğŸ›¡ï¸ Defense Strategies for Each Stage</h4>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 5px; margin-top: 15px;">
        <div style="background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
