        </div>
        <div style="background: #2980b9; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
            <h6>2. Weaponize</h6>
            <small>Application whitelisting</small>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #1abc9c; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
            <h6>3. Delivery</h6>
            <small>Email filtering</small>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #16a085; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
