                            <h5>DNS-Based Filtering</h5>
                            <ul>
                                <li><b>How it works:</b> Blocks domain resolution</li>
                                <li><b>Pros:</b> Simple, fast, covers all devices</li>
                                <li><b>Cons:</b> Easy to bypass with alternative DNS</li>
                                <li><b>Tools:</b> Pi-hole, OpenDNS, custom DNS servers</li>
                                <li><b>Effectiveness:</b> Good for basic filtering</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
                            <h5>Proxy-Based Filtering</h5>
                            <ul>
                                <li><b>How it works:</b> Intercepts and inspects web traffic</li>
                                <li><b>Pros:</b> Deep inspection, SSL decryption</li>
                                <li><b>Cons:</b> Performance impact, complex setup</li>
                                <li><b>Tools:</b> Squid, Blue Coat, Websense</li>
