                <h3>Building DC-01: Domain Controller</h3>
                <div style="background-color: #fff0f0; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 10px;">
                    <h4>ğŸ‘‘ Step-by-Step: Windows Server 2022 Domain Controller</h4>
                    
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4A90E2;">
                        <h5>Step 1: Create VM & Install OS</h5>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Create new VM: 4 GB RAM, 70 GB disk (dynamic)</li>
                            <li>Install Windows Server 2022 Standard (Desktop Experience)</li>
                            <li>Set computer name: <code>DC-01</code></li>
                            <li>Set static IP: <code>10.0.99.10/24</code>, gateway: <code>10.0.99.1</code></li>
                            <li>DNS: <code>127.0.0.1</code> (will be DC itself)</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #5cb85c;">
                        <h5>Step 2: Promote to Domain Controller</h5>
                        <pre style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
                # Install Active Directory Domain Services
                Install-WindowsFeature AD-Domain-Services -IncludeManagementTools

                # Promote server to domain controller
                Install-ADDSForest '
                    -DomainName "techcorp.local" '
                    -DomainNetbiosName "TECHCORP" '
                    -ForestMode "WinThreshold" '
                    -DomainMode "WinThreshold" '
                    -SafeModeAdministratorPassword (ConvertTo-SecureString "P@ssw0rd123!" -AsPlainText -Force) '
                    -Force
                        </pre>
